==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Membered
<hw>Mem"bered</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Having
limbs; -- chiefly used in composition.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Her.)</fld> <def>Having legs of a different
tincture from that of the body; -- said of a bird in heraldic
representations.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Membership</ent>⟦br⟧
